Customer
- customisation of burger
  - As a customer, I would like to be able to customise my burger so that my preferences are reflected in my food.
- additional ingredients
  - As a customer, I want to be able to add specified ingredients to my choice of burger so that I can have more of one ingredient on my burger.
- sides
  - As a customer, I want to be able to choose what sides to have alongside my burger so that I have additional food based on my preferences.
- cost
  - As a customer, I would like to be able to see the cost of my burger so that I can determine if I can afford the meal or not.
- order ID
  - As a customer, I want to receive an order ID so that I can track which order is mine.


Service Staff
- status of order
  - As a service staff employee, I want to have access to the status of each order so that I know what orders are complete.
- add/remove orders
  - As a service staff employee, I would like to be able to add and remove orders so that I can provide accurate service to my customers.


Stock Staff
- view number or stocks
  - As an inventory staff member, I wish to have access to the viewing of stocks so that I can see how much stock is left.
- reorder/replenish inventory
  - As an inventory staff member, I want to be able to reorder and replenish my stocks so that I always have sufficient resources.
- reduce the amount of items accordingly
  - As an inventory staff member, I want to be able to deduct the inventory level as a customer places an order so I know the correct amount of inventory we have.
